Package: yuri
Type: Package
Title: Download research data
Description: Download research data with an URI such as a DOI or HDL. Intended to work with Dataverse, CKAN, Dryad, Zenodo, and Figshare APIs such that the data can be included into reproducible workflows.
Version: 0.2-5
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr, archive, jsonlite
Date: 2025-08-08
Encoding: UTF-8
